by DHager at 2018-01-09T10:50:07Z

@nicolas-grekas In this scenario, the PHP code is running on a Linux container, sectioned off inside a Linux virtual machine, which in turn is running within a Windows physical host.

Even if you could detect the situation, that's probably the kind of stuff which should exist in a separate library or utility.

A possible compromise: ASCII art :)

